  "detailed_description": "The Chaos Gene is a classic 1v1 inspired fighting game. This is a indie passion project Inspired by classic fighting game series like Street Fighter, KOF, Killer Instinct and Guilty Gear & MK. I hope to provide players with a new gaming experience with the nostalgia of the classic fighting games. It is being released in early access so I can get support and feedback from the community to help polish and balance the game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures Available now<br />\r\n8 Playable Characters<br />\r\n14 Stages<br />\r\nLocal Versus Mode <br />\r\nVs CPU<br />\r\nTraining Mode<br />\r\n<br />\r\nComing Soon<br />\r\n20 Total playable characters<br />\r\nStory Mode<br />\r\nChallenges Mode<br />\r\nOnline Multiplayer (RollBack)",
  "about_the_game": "The Chaos Gene is a classic 1v1 inspired fighting game. This is a indie passion project Inspired by classic fighting game series like Street Fighter, KOF, Killer Instinct and Guilty Gear & MK. I hope to provide players with a new gaming experience with the nostalgia of the classic fighting games. It is being released in early access so I can get support and feedback from the community to help polish and balance the game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures Available now<br />\r\n8 Playable Characters<br />\r\n14 Stages<br />\r\nLocal Versus Mode <br />\r\nVs CPU<br />\r\nTraining Mode<br />\r\n<br />\r\nComing Soon<br />\r\n20 Total playable characters<br />\r\nStory Mode<br />\r\nChallenges Mode<br />\r\nOnline Multiplayer (RollBack)",
